immediate_step_1 = Check her temperature to see how high her fever is, and try to give her a child's dose of acetaminophen.;
immediate_step_2 = Do not give her aspirin, but try putting a cool washcloth on her forehead.;
comfort_method = Always make her talk about her feelings and ask her what she wants to talk about, even if she says she doesn't feel like talking.;
when_to_worry = If she still feels very hot under her armpits after an hour or begins breathing really hard and fast.;
future_preparation = Always keep some medication on hand and flag down a neighbor or friend when you hear someone crying unexpectedly.
